title: Is The Pressure All On James Harden?
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss the pressure on James Harden to deliver title to Philly, do Jaylen Brown and Jayson Tatum make Celtics legit contenders in East, Ben Simmons thinks new-look Nets will be scary, Giannis drops a hot & spicy 50-piece on Pacers, Jacoby says KD is best player in NBA, plus what’s next for Tom Brady. All that and more!!!
